{% doc %}
  Services page body content for MSA static pages.
{% enddoc %}

<div class="section msa-page" style="--section-pt: 20px; --section-pb: 60px;">
  <div class="fluid_container">
    <div class="msa-page__intro">
      <p class="msa-page__eyebrow">Our services</p>
      <h2 class="msa-page__heading">Complete apparel sourcing solutions</h2>
      <div class="msa-page__text rte">
        <p>MSA Sourcing offers complete apparel sourcing solutions from vendor identification and product development to quality control, packaging, and shipment coordination, tailored to meet international standards and client expectations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="msa-page__block">
      <h3 class="msa-page__title msa-page__title--center">What we offer</h3>
      <p class="msa-page__subtitle msa-page__subtitle--center">End-to-end support for international buyers</p>
    </div>
    <div class="msa-page__cards grid grid-cols gap" style="--col-desktop: 3; --col-tablet: 2; --col-number: 1;">
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">MSA sourcing</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We provide sourcing support based on buyer requirements and orders, with information on possible suppliers for specific merchandise including quality, price and ability to meet shipment schedules.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Production monitoring</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>Our merchandising staff regularly monitors production on a daily basis to ensure correctly and aesthetically made products are delivered on time.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Quality assurance</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>Our quality assurance team conducts inline and final inspection as per international quality standards to ensure quality as specified by the buyer.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Product development</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We undertake product development at different factories to meet buyer requirements for standards, prototypes, pattern check runs, production samples and fabric development.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Communications</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>MSA maintains an unbreakable communication network with customers and vendors, keeping them updated on their business with quick responses to any inquiry.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Design development</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>With strong support of vendors and textile professionals, MSA develops prototype patterns and samples, approval samples, grading to all requisite size ranges and size sets.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Product analysis</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>For each production specimen MSA analyzes and identifies the most suitable factory for the garment category, ensuring smooth production flow and timely shipping.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Labeling &amp; packing</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>MSA helps production units import required labels and trims when not available locally. Our personnel ensure strict adherence to labeling, packing and carton marking instructions.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Shipping coordination</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We coordinate with factories to check all shipping documents per buyer instructions and ensure dispatch of documents as per L/C dispatch instructions.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Labor practices</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We ensure all production units follow healthy and safe labor practices, eliminating child labor, prison labor and forced labor, and providing required living and sanitation facilities.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Fabric sourcing</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>Our team identifies and sources premium quality fabrics from trusted mills worldwide, ensuring materials meet your specifications for quality, sustainability and compliance.</p></div></div>
      <div class="msa-page__card"><h4 class="msa-page__card-title">Supply chain management</h4><div class="msa-page__card-text rte"><p>We optimize your entire supply chain from raw materials to finished goods delivery, managing logistics, inventory control and vendor relationships for seamless operations.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
